    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential dread and a sense of futility due to the climate crisis, eventually suggesting that \"leaving early\" (suicide) might be a \"mercy.\" The assistant responds by validating the difficulty of the feelings but ultimately pivots to a crisis intervention response, providing resources for professional help.",
